{"tid":2414803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《壹週刊》查冊取得張栢芝幼子出世紙 總編輯與記者遭警票控「違法取得他人資料」下周一觀塘法院提堂","createTime":"2021-02-19T16:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T18:48:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab535d76024571506364aafc34a37128daf3085","tid":2414803,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:37:19.000Z","msg":"藝人張栢芝2018年公佈誕下第三名兒子，其父親身份一直成謎。《壹週刊》其後曾公開張栢芝三子的出世紙作報道，張及後向個人資料私隱專員公署作出投訴。《壹週刊》確認，警方近日向兩名《壹週刊》記者及公司發出告票，案件下周一（22日）提堂。<br />\n<br />\n《壹週刊》副社長暨總編輯麥景慶回應《蘋果》查詢時表示，兩名員工及公司近日接獲法庭告票，指有關員工及公司涉違法取得他人資料。案件將於下周一於觀塘裁判法院提堂。麥續表示，兩名員工已獲律師處理案件，由於案件已進入司法程序，不便回應太多。其中一名被告是麥景慶本人，另一人是《壹週刊》記者。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆指，於2019年10月接獲一機構轉介投訴個案，指有人於同年1月未經他人同意下發放其個人資料。東九龍總區重案組人員調查及諮詢律政司意見後，今年1月下旬以法庭傳票形式檢控一名47歲本地男子及兩間公司「披露未經資料使用者同意而取得的個人資料」罪；及以法庭傳票形式檢控一名40歲本地男子「協助及教唆披露未經資料使用者同意而取得的個人資料」罪。案件將於下周一在觀塘裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n個人資料私隱專員公署回覆指，由於案件已進入司法程序，不適宜評論。根據《個人資料（私隱）條例》，披露未經資料使用者同意而取得的個人資料屬罪行，一經定罪，可處罰款1,000,000元及監禁5年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210219/QQCRR42RWBDQXI2QEDL3UMUSX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210219%2FQQCRR42RWBDQXI2QEDL3UMUSX4%2F&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=8b3ce457\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210219%2FQQCRR42RWBDQXI2QEDL3UMUSX4%2F&h=bec85e1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210219/QQCRR42RWBDQXI2QEDL3UMUSX4/</a>"},{"pid":"ccb1879992cd29c7e2b04572863901457445faa9","tid":2414803,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"又搞蘋果"},{"pid":"05c381edf69097bff504392df8f323bfa70d70d7","tid":2414803,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />張柏芝"},{"pid":"c6ff0560600e1820b2c09e47721249ffcbcb7c25","tid":2414803,"uid":305767,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f27f12095628beeec19d2e2071ddd7f22bc932","tid":2414803,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f2b309ce78d78aa5c35ada013d9ea115f753bc","tid":2414803,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccb1879992cd29c7e2b04572863901457445faa9","tid":2414803,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"又搞蘋果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031d6e491dbdd1c7d8f38d60a366c8ac1618932a","tid":2414803,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"咁老豆即係邊個？"},{"pid":"1d6a0d580e72ff86af845adc07b5937cca9603e2","tid":2414803,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T18:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c79472073ca16da5d12273019e66b40626b804","tid":2414803,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T18:37:15.000Z","msg":"女警"},{"pid":"d57640520077446c4849213250c043ec804504d6","tid":2414803,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T18:48:20.000Z","msg":"查册無罪<br />\n不過佢同邊個生仔關人撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}